              </DEFINITION>
              <THE-VALUE><xhtml:div><xhtml:p><xhtml:strong>FTS5 virtual tables</xhtml:strong> enabling search across specification content.</xhtml:p></xhtml:div></THE-VALUE>
            </ATTRIBUTE-VALUE-XHTML>
